Package nl.naturalis.geneious.util

Utility classes.
Author:
Ayco Holleman
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    APDList
    A subclass of ArrayList with AnnotatedPluginDocument as type argument.
    CommonStatistics
    Utility class aimed at providing statistics for operations that deal with CSV-like files.
    DocumentUtils
    Various methods related to Geneious documents.
    JsonUtil
    Provides method for serializing objects to JSON.
    Messages
    Common messages emitted by all operations.
    NaturalisIcons
    Provides differently sized and differently colored Naturalis icons.
    Ping
    Pings the database to ascertain that all documents have been indexed.
    PingHistory
    Generates and saves unique ping values that are inserted as extract IDs into special, temporary documents.
    PingSequence
    An extension of DefaultNucleotideSequence solely meant to create "ping documents".
    PreconditionValidator
    Checks whether the preconditions for an operation (e"g" a BOLD import) are satisfied.
    QueryUtils
    Methods for querying the Geneious database.
    RuntimeSettings
    This class is currently only used for the AB1/Fasta Import operation and facilitates a custom way of requesting and storing user preferences.
    StoredDocumentComparator
    Sorts StoredDocument instances according to the document version (descending).
    StoredDocumentList
    Extension of ArrayList with StoredDocument as concrete type argument.
    StoredDocumentTable<K>
    An extension of HashMap that maps some property of a StoredDocument to a list of StoredDocument instances sharing the same value for that property.
